Title: 115: Application of Geospatial Analytics to Business and Real Life
Description:
In this episode of the SuperDataScience Podcast, I chat with Data Scientist, Neelabh Pant. You will hear about the indexing of spatial databases, learn about the disruptive innovation with data science, and learn how to create models to solve everyday problems.


If you enjoyed this episode, check out show notes, resources, and more at www.superdatascience.com/115
